---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Bayern Kapital Participates in Seed Financing Round of parcelLab - parcelLab"
  description="Bayern Kapital and four business angels invest a high six-figure amount in Munich-based parcelLab to fuel development, sales, and international expansion."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company News</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">Bayern Kapital Participates in Seed Financing Round of parcelLab</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2016-10-01">October 1, 2016</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>3 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Landshut/Munich, August 31, 2016 -- Munich-based tech startup parcelLab GmbH successfully closed a seed financing round. Bayern Kapital and four business angels invested a high six-figure amount, with capital allocated toward development, sales, and international expansion.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Company Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          parcelLab supports online retailers by optimizing the delivery experience. The platform detects shipping delays through an innovative algorithm and communicates proactively with customers via email or SMS. Rather than relying on shipping providers for communication, retailers maintain direct contact through personalized messages in their brand style.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          The solution also provides logistics performance analytics, revealing discrepancies between service level agreements and actual delivery performance.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Key Benefits</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">30--40% reduction</strong> in customer inquiries</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Additional marketing touchpoints created through shipping communications</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Revenue generated through untapped sales potential</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Reduced logistics and customer service costs</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Investor Quote</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"parcelLab offers clear technological and financial added value in a growing market segment."</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Roman Huber, Managing Director, Bayern Kapital</p>
        </div>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Founder Quote</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"Our technology provides a decisive competitive advantage to many retailers in e-commerce."</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Anton Eder, Founder and CEO, parcelLab</p>
        </div>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Bayern Kapital, Bavaria's venture capital company, manages eleven investment funds worth approximately 340 million euros. The seed financing round marked an early milestone in parcelLab's journey to become a leading post-purchase experience platform.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
